			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Speak to Ceres Olsin - S_GLO_IronThrone_Group1_Prisoner2 ced0a558-b5ed-4493-a499-1890ec48fbfb - (-58; 37; 71)  in the Dock warehouse after saving them.\r\n\r\nQuick setup:\r\n- Load CTY_Main_A\r\n- Use Debug Book (Ctrl + Shift + 9)\r\n- Set Quest Flags and Options -> Act3 (LOW) -> Iron Throne -> Change State -> Back At Docks -> MajoritySaved\r\n- Then talk to the NPC"
